{"tid":2109448,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被控襲警 庭上播片  群警壓住浴血被告 雙棍交叉架頸","createTime":"2020-07-15T08:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T09:17:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9136957cdc3c5252709a03f45c835864a4956287","tid":2109448,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200715/P3B7JFRK6JSGNEN7R2KGAT3MMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200715%2FP3B7JFRK6JSGNEN7R2KGAT3MMA%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu1A4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=b4c83b30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200715%2FP3B7JFRK6JSGNEN7R2KGAT3MMA%2F&h=b347aad0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200715/P3B7JFRK6JSGNEN7R2KGAT3MMA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n被控襲警 庭上播片 <br />\n群警壓住浴血被告 雙棍交叉架頸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ha1Zr0NkFaNPf3pJZpB8tYFes9U=/1968x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/554PTBW6KYGJQXTLQ3D5DGK7HI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fha1Zr0NkFaNPf3pJZpB8tYFes9U%3D%2F1968x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F554PTBW6KYGJQXTLQ3D5DGK7HI.jpg&h=62d6536e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n片段顯示被告當日遭兩名警員以警棍交叉架頸。SocREC片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民間集會團隊今年1月在遮打花園舉行「天下制裁」集會，中途遭警方腰斬。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n機場特警A昨獲法庭頒令匿名。他稱。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑用罐打頭 「兜頭」淋水<br />\n<br />\n被告在地上遭制服時，A稱。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/myI3quK0Xqj2fU0jpLGojfkAlXc=/1898x1897/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ORVR45CMX64DYI6HDDNQSX725Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmyI3quK0Xqj2fU0jpLGojfkAlXc%3D%2F1898x1897%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FORVR45CMX64DYI6HDDNQSX725Y.jpg&h=f4d75067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當日被告被捕時頭破血流，狀甚痛苦。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n辯方播片，顯示被告遭至少三名警員壓在地上，臉部朝天，地下有血迹，其中兩警以警棍交叉架被告的頸。A承認被告沒持武器及佩戴護具，也沒攻擊或挑釁他人。辯方指實情是A推被告，而非被告推他。A否認。<br />\n<br />\nA承認當時持警棍，惟否認在被告面前揮動警棍或制服被告時曾用警棍。A同意片中警員曾上下搖動罐狀物和被告頭部向地，惟看不到罐狀物有否接觸被告。A否認被告遭制服時曾說：「唔好㩒我喺地下，我個頭流緊血，受緊傷。」A亦否認被告曾報稱頭暈要求治理，同袍曾用水「兜頭淋」他致全身濕透。A稱發現被告頭部受傷後，曾着同袍為他包紮。<br />\n<br />\n同屬機場特警的李煒杰接受辯方盤問時承認看不到被告拳打A，只目睹他們糾纏。李亦承認被告遭同袍淋水，但稱是同袍應被告要求清洗頭部血迹。案件表證成立，聆訊周四續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC180/20"},{"pid":"08dba2573e672abf861bca8684d0eef458f2b4a8","tid":2109448,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:49:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c993787af938db0626d238461b969975aa93a03d","tid":2109448,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7c369d2c35afd98062f94b6a2e2d08a3761ac4","tid":2109448,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea663668dd91b2fd4483dcc69cd93843df6eb47","tid":2109448,"uid":350350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:53:44.000Z","msg":"仲要表證成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d2e54e95d4305849c2a0a8b1b9d21aed2f24ac","tid":2109448,"uid":50608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ea663668dd91b2fd4483dcc69cd93843df6eb47","tid":2109448,"uid":350350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:53:44.000Z","msg":"仲要表證成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"rep